reviewText: I'd love to have this, but I have not purchased this ever...
It's not suitable for all DVD players and when I reached out for a refund, no one ever got back to me...

This box set containing 20 classic Woody Allen movies is a dream for fans of this hilarious director's work. We've been watching these films across about 6 months and still aren't through all of them
A marvelous collection at a good price.
The package is great, it includes many movies for a reasonable price, and I haven't had a problem playing them on my multi-region DVD player (in Mexico). It was definitely a good choice!
a chronological list would be helpful-but thank you IMDB
